{"title":"Android Note 1","date":"2018-12-04T06:00:55.000Z","slug":"androidDay1","comments":true,"categories":["Android Note"],"updated":"2019-01-14T09:45:57.234Z","content":"<p>Day 1:<br>\nfollow <a href=\"https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/build-your-first-android-app-kotlin/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">build-your-first-android-app-kotlin</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"check-view-id\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#check-view-id\">¶</a>Check view ID</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">val showCountTextView = findViewById&lt;TextView&gt;(R.id.counter)</span><br><span class=\"line\">val buttonID: button = findViewById(R.id.button)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"interactive-with-button\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#interactive-with-button\">¶</a>Interactive with button</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>By listener:</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">toast_button.setOnClickListener &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .......</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>By layout xml and function</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"a-simple-kotlin-function\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#a-simple-kotlin-function\">¶</a>A simple Kotlin function:</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun countMe (view: View) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ......</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>arguments: (variable name: variable type = default value)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>what is the variable type of “view: View”?</p>\n<p>view: the objects in activity (like TextView, Button, …)<br>\ndue to we use &quot;android: onClick=“xxx” &quot; in the layout xml files for buttons, we need this argument!</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"kotlin-string\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#kotlin-string\">¶</a>Kotlin string:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>concatenate:</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">val a = &quot;Hello&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">val b = &quot;World&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = &quot;$a $b&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = a + b   // same as calling operator function a.plus(b)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">val sb = StringBuilder()</span><br><span class=\"line\">sb.append(a).append(b)</span><br><span class=\"line\">val c = sb.toString()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>string to Int (or other):</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>count: Int </span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">### Second activity</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- add a new activity from</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">```main-&gt;java-&gt;com.xxx...-&gt;(right click)-&gt;New</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>check activity status from “AndroidManifest.xml”</li>\n<li>go to the new activity and send some info:</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun go_to_act2(view: View)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   val act2 = Intent(this, Main2Activity::class.java)</span><br><span class=\"line\">   act2.putExtra(Main2Activity.mainActNum, count.toString())</span><br><span class=\"line\">   startActivity(act2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>receive the info in the new activity:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>create a static object</li>\n</ul>\n  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">companion object &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       const val mainActNum = &quot;wtf&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>receive from intent</li>\n</ul>\n  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">fun getMainActValue(view: View)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       val myIntent = intent</span><br><span class=\"line\">       val count = myIntent.getStringExtra(mainActNum)</span><br><span class=\"line\">       Second_view_text.text = count</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"HackMd 語法測試","slug":"HackMdTest"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/androidDay1/"}